body:
`span` has the following syntax:

```javascript
{
   $search: {
     "index": <index name>, // optional, defaults to "default"
     "span": {
       "term" | <positional-operator>": {
         <operator-specification>
       }
     }
   }
}
```

> **Note:** `span` search queries can't use the [compound](compound-ref)
> operator.
